      • TYPE_MUSIC

        public static final int TYPE_MUSIC
        All the music files from the external storage. READ_STORAGE permission is required for this type. Application can set the type using addRingtoneType(int).
        See Also:
        addRingtoneType(int), Constant Field Values

      • TYPE_DEFAULT

        public static final int TYPE_DEFAULT
        This type will add a row at the top of the list with "Default" label. Whenever user selects "Default", it will return ringtone that is selected in the settings of the phone. Application can set the type using addRingtoneType(int).
        See Also:
        addRingtoneType(int), Constant Field Values

      • TYPE_SILENT

        public static final int TYPE_SILENT
        This type will add a row at the top of the list with "Silent" label. Whenever user selects "Silent", it indicates that user don't want to add any ringtone. Application can set the type using addRingtoneType(int).
        See Also:
        addRingtoneType(int), Constant Field Values
